snippet.title: Fred Davis
snippet.description: Fred Davis is an independent, nondual, spiritual unteacher. He is the creator of The Living Method of Spiritual Awakening, which has introduced hundreds of people around the world to their True Nature. He is also the creator and editor of the popular website, AwakeningClarityNow.com and the podcast Fred Davis' Nondual Teaching at AwakeningClarityNow.com/podbean. He is also the author of five books: Beyond Recovery: Nonduality and the Twelve Steps, The Book of Undoing: Direct Pointing to Nondual Awareness,  The Book of Unknowing: From Enlightenment to Embodiment, The Book of Unveiling: From Awakening to Abidance, and Awaken Now: The Living Method of Spiritual Awakening. Private Awakening Sessions and Clarity Sessions are available through his website.
